room_title: Escape room "Gangster’s Gamble" by Team Vs Time in Chicago
room_description: Travel back to the time when mafia and gangs ruled the cities, and government officials were desperately trying to keep them in check. Your detective unit has to go undercover to infiltrate the most notorious crime family, the Ferrettis. Find substantial evidence against the gangsters before they sniff you out. And you know what they do to rats…
